item.title: CVE-2024-47045|2024-09-26T06:22:26.091Z -- national%20tax%20agency -- the%20installer%20of%20e-tax%20software%28common%20program%29
item.description: Privilege chaining issue exists in the installer of e-Tax software(common program). If this vulnerability is exploited, a malicious DLL prepared by an attacker may be executed with higher privileges than the application privilege.
